","The Greek yoghurt can be stored in the fridge for 7-10 days (at a temperature below 4°C).","Use the last 200 g of this homemade yoghurt as a new starter to make your next batch of homemade yoghurt."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","18h 30m","1 total recipe"]}